            "title": "警油麻地搗毒品快餐車  揭「波棍」下藏逾百包可卡因太空油等  男司機被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3439221079b431accf0f31bec9ffb386/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032804334389343.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>油麻地搗破毒品快餐車。周五（<b>28</b>日）凌晨<b>2</b>時許，警方在新填地街與咸美頓街一帶巡邏期間，發現一輛停在路邊的私家車形迹可疑，遂上前向正狀似等人的男司機問話，隨後對車輛進行搜查，在俗稱「波棍」的車速控制桿下發現暗格，內藏67包可卡因、20多包「K仔」、13包冰毒和4粒太空油。警員當場拘捕男司機，他被黑布蒙頭帶走。\n\n</p>\n<p>據了解，被捕<b>35</b>歲男子報稱是<b> Uber</b>司機。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162817/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在油麻地搗破毒品快餐車。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a3ce0c5f0aa78b72f217d4669b64a50f/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-03-27_at_8_38_27_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在油麻地搗破毒品快餐車。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162811/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方對車輛進行搜查。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a157688f4f5d2514e46b1337813bb958/2025-03/34_4.jpe